sequenceDiagram
    participant DeploySH as deploy.sh<br/>(Init Container)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>(opendatahub operator)
    participant Prom as RHODS Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant OcpProm as OpenShift Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant Components as Component Metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant BBE as Blackbox Exporter<br/>9114/TCP HTTPS
    participant AM as Alertmanager<br/>10443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PD as PagerDuty<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SMTP as SMTP Server<br/>TLS STARTTLS
    participant DMS as Dead Man's Snitch<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over DeploySH,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Platform Bootstrap

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>(redhat-ods-applications,<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring,<br/>rhods-notebooks)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Namespaces created

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Apply CRDs<br/>(OdhApplication, OdhDocument,<br/>OdhQuickStart, OdhDashboardConfig)
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: CRDs applied

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Create KfDef CRs<br/>(dashboard, nbc, model-mesh,<br/>dspo, monitoring, anaconda)
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: KfDef CRs created

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Apply Dashboard CRs<br/>(OdhApplication ISV tiles,<br/>OdhDashboardConfig,<br/>OdhDocument, OdhQuickStart)
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Dashboard CRs applied

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Deploy monitoring stack<br/>(Prometheus, Alertmanager,<br/>Blackbox Exporter)
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Monitoring deployed

    DeploySH->>K8sAPI: Apply NetworkPolicies<br/>+ Pod Security RBAC
    K8sAPI-->>DeploySH: Security resources applied

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch KfDef CRs
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: KfDef events
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Reconcile: deploy components<br/>(dashboard, notebooks,<br/>model-mesh, DSPO, anaconda)

    Note over Prom,DMS: Flow 2: Monitoring Data Pipeline (managed service)

    Prom->>OcpProm: Federation scrape<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    OcpProm-->>Prom: haproxy, controller_runtime,<br/>resource metrics

    Prom->>Components: Scrape metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None
    Components-->>Prom: Component metrics<br/>(notebook-ctrl, model-ctrl,<br/>modelmesh-ctrl, DSPO, operator)

    BBE->>K8sAPI: Probe endpoints<br/>(dashboard, notebook spawner, DSPO)
    K8sAPI-->>BBE: Probe results

    Prom->>AM: Fire alerts<br/>9093/TCP HTTP plaintext
    AM->>PD: Critical alerts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service Key
    AM->>SMTP: User notifications<br/>Auth: SMTP credentials
    AM->>DMS: Heartbeat<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: URL secret<br/>(every 5 min)
